	<div id="donationLetter">Dear Alumni and Fans,<br><br>Joining ski team was the most rewarding activity I was involved in during my time at Carolina. The team was still young back then. That meant we could really make it what we wanted. I learned a lot along the way and I found a group of people that loved to get outdoors and tear up some slopes. Some of the traditions that we started back then have carried on and enriched the ski team. That is something I very much enjoy to see, and I would like to continue to enrich the team as it progresses. If ski team was a rewarding experience for you, consider donating to the undergraduate team.<br><br>All donations go to the <a href="Scholarshipspage.html">UNCSSTAlumni Organization Scholarship</a> for undergraduate team members.<br><br>Sincerely,<br><br>Seth D. Muller<br><br><br></div>
